{"tid":1564991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方拒提供醫療報告手令　高院受理傷者司法覆核申請","createTime":"2019-09-13T03:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T03:36:52.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a7f77fabf2c26fd083947b842df89092f128a502","tid":1564991,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:32:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480345-20190913.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480345-20190913.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmOzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=913f4709\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480345-20190913.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2d3ac3d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480345-20190913.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n上月反修例抗議期間爆發警民衝突，有傷者不滿警方拒絕提供取得醫療報告手令的資料，提出司法覆核許可申請。高等法院早上頒下書面判詞，批准申請人的司法覆核申請。<br />\n<br />\n法官林雲浩在判詞中表示，昨日聽取控辯雙方陳詞後，認為案件存在可爭辯的理據，因此批准申請。"},{"pid":"51f888650deb4ed6a7c20b15c3945c80c3366300","tid":1564991,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:33:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZ